<p>The <code>@notLast</code> property returns TRUE if this is NOT the last iteration.</p>

<h2>Pipe-Separated List</h2>
<pre>{open}colors{close}
  {open}$colors{close}{open}@notLast ? |{close}
{open}/colors{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<p>
{colors}
  {$colors}{@notLast ? |}
{/colors}
</p>

<h2>Add Separator Between Items</h2>
<pre>{open}users{close}
  {open}$name{close}
  {open}@notLast{close}&lt;hr&gt;{open}/@notLast{close}
{open}/users{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<div style="border:1px solid #ccc; padding:10px;">
{users}
  {$name}
  {@notLast}<hr>{/@notLast}
{/users}
</div>
